name: marine-seismic-reflection-profiles-data-of-san-francisco-bay-area302d0
notes: Dataset consists of two-dimensional marine seismic reflection profile data from the San Francisco Bay area. These data were acquired in 1995, with the vessel Robert Gray. The USGS identifier for these data is G295SF. For more information on the seismic surveys see http://walrus.wr.usgs.gov/infobank/g/g295sf/html/g-2-95-sf.meta.html These data are also available via GeoMapApp (http://www.geomapapp.org/) and Virtual Ocean ( http://www.virtualocean.org/) earth science exploration and visualization applications.
